::Spears::

She didn't make a sound, but she gave a deep sparked sigh.  She 
looked at Striker and realized that they would never get a moment of 
peace as long as the war was going on.  She smiled to Striker, "We 
are needed yet again to fight the evils on this planet.  Well, if 
this keeps up, we won't need to practice." she said with a light 
chuckle.  She leaned over and kissed Striker on the cheek.
